      <h2 class="h2">Organisation Registration</h2>
      <p>The network includes organisations from across different sectors that provide useful services for people who are homeless. As a trusted source of information, the local network set minimum standards around who is included - see our standards toolkit for information on the criteria we use in Manchester.</p>
      <a href="/about/organisations/" class="btn btn--brand-d btn--in-copy"><span class="btn__text">Register Your Organisation</span></a>

      <h2 class="h2">Information Quality</h2>
      <p>Please note, all information is provided by organisations in the network, so while we make every effort to ensure it is kept up to date, we can't always guarantee the accuracy of information that is entered by third parties. Please <a href="/contact">get in touch</a> if you spot anything that is incorrect or missing.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--brand-d btn--in-copy"><span class="btn__text">Tell us about an issue</span></a>
