      <h2 class="h2">Our Team</h2>
      <p>We have a small core team of 4 people based in Manchester, 2 of which have recent lived experience of homelessness. Each city also has a local network and co-ordinator, and we are supported by a network of digital experts and volunteers.</p>
      <a href="/about/our-team/" class="btn btn--brand-d btn--in-copy"><span class="btn__text">Our Team</span></a>

      <p>We use research, co-production, human centered design and creative technology to develop online tools that make it easier for people experiencing homelessness to get help. We also facilitate discussion and co-production, and work behind the scenes to connect the network. Here is a little story of where this idea came from: <a href="/about/how-this-started/">How this started.</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
