      <h2 class="h2">Co-production and Partnership</h2>
      <p>Co-production is central to everything we do, and we are proud to support the <a href="/about/manchester-homelessness-partnership">Manchester Homelessness Partnership</a> in ensuring people with lived experience are meaningfully engaged in designing and delivering services.<p>
      <a href="/about/manchester-homelessness-partnership" class="btn btn--brand-d btn--in-copy">
