      <h2 class="h2">Our Organisation</h2>
      <p>We are a not for profit company, currently waiting for our official charity status. We have been funded so far by donations from local philanthropists, friends, small grants, a loan from KeyFund, and business sponsorship. We always pay at least the real living wage for the area. We are an open and transparent organisation, so please get in touch if you have any further questions.</p>
      <p>In order to continue to develop and improve this central resource, and to facilitate change through the network, we are looking for businesses to sponsor us to help grow out team, providing more opportunities for people who have experienced homelessness. If you are interested in supporting us, please contact Gary at <a href="mailto:gary@streetsupport.net">gary@streetsupport.net</a>, or on 07824 667709.</p>

